{"tid":975662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡南亞男墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-01-09T22:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T23:05:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6438cefee5c00a9e9b3848e3e71937eeb477a7","tid":975662,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:31:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190110/59125508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59125508&d=oz01qc%2FeAqoMtsiDFJ7X6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4cb65040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59125508&h=33e9b37e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190110/59125508</a><br />\n紅磡湖光街7號鴻運閣，凌晨4時35分，一名南亞男子從高處墮下，倒臥地上昏迷，途人發現報警。救護員接報到場，證實墮樓男子已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查發現，男事主與家人同住15樓，早前曾與妻子爭吵。據稱，他受工作壓力問題困擾，警方調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=oz01qc%2FeAqoMtsiDFJ7X6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d699b6c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"e8996df1359b4408d371175a576e9d7eb62b3718","tid":975662,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T22:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減一"},{"pid":"8b490bd86db8e055501f547d183c2e71f14ece25","tid":975662,"uid":280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTi